cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper discusses the modeling and optimization of Deep Neural Networks, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
